{"id":454,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":56,"title":"56. To Buy a Birthday Present","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":10,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present.454/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/0-56-to-buy-a-birthday-present.mp3","transcript":"What are you getting Jim for his birthday?\nI don't know yet.\nYou can always get him a shirt.\nBut I got him one last year.\nOh, that's right. Let me think.\nI want to get him something different.\nHow about a briefcase?\nGood idea! His briefcase is getting old.\nAnd it's something he'll use every day.\nOf course! Why didn't I think of that?","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:50","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"What are you getting Jim for his birthday?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/1.mp3","time_start":3.32,"time_end":5.32},{"position":2,"content":"I don't know yet.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/2.mp3","time_start":5.32,"time_end":6.64},{"position":3,"content":"You can always get him a shirt.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/3.mp3","time_start":6.64,"time_end":8.24},{"position":4,"content":"But I got him one last year.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/4.mp3","time_start":8.24,"time_end":10.24},{"position":5,"content":"Oh, that's right. Let me think.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/5.mp3","time_start":10.24,"time_end":12.75},{"position":6,"content":"I want to get him something different.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/6.mp3","time_start":12.78,"time_end":14.73},{"position":7,"content":"How about a briefcase?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/7.mp3","time_start":14.73,"time_end":16.1},{"position":8,"content":"Good idea! His briefcase is getting old.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/8.mp3","time_start":16.1,"time_end":18.63},{"position":9,"content":"And it's something he'll use every day.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/9.mp3","time_start":18.63,"time_end":20.62},{"position":10,"content":"Of course! Why didn't I think of that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/56-to-buy-a-birthday-present-2022-03-07-21-23-22/10.mp3","time_start":20.62,"time_end":23.11}]}